    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": ">The symbols would have to be cross mod and even cross-genre\r\n\r\nIf they are decorations then they don't, because decorations are replaceable by the modder.\r\n\r\nI don't remember RA2 having stances. Area Guarding is the closest thing I can think of and that had no visual feedback from the unit.\r\n\r\nI also prefer the colored selection box method because of the less UI clutter, tbh. I am fine with introducing decorations in the main mods though, as long as you promise you wouldn't object another PR introducing the selectioncolorstances."
